    - target: {fileID: 4604026737904347161, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: Crate + loot system
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'These crates can be found everywhere. They always contain loot like
        the items we saw right before.


        Also, so you know,  the item they
        will drop depends on your stats like your health and your ammo number: The
        less you have, the more chance you have to get some.


        Punch the
        crate just like you did with the door toto destroy it and reveal the item
        inside!

        But be warned, breaking them will do noise all around, attracting
        enemies. This one is in a safe place but be careful with others!'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_margin.z
      value: 1.417953
