      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'And finally we have a makeshift knife.


        This will also be
        usefull when an enemy is in close combat with you.


        These knife
        do high damages but they are not infitite. They have a durability that you
        can see on bottom-right corner, just above your ammo, along with the number
        of knives you have in your inventory.


        So use it with caution.'
